data_for_metrics = UK_distritos_merge_2[selected_variables_new_std].copy()
data_for_metrics = data_for_metrics.replace([np.inf, -np.inf], np.nan)
data_for_metrics.dropna(inplace=True)
labels_hc_ag6_wknn8 = UK_distritos_merge_2.loc[data_for_metrics.index, "hc_ag6_wknn8"]
labels_hc_ag6 = UK_distritos_merge_2.loc[data_for_metrics.index, "hc_ag6"]
fit_scores = []
for cluster_col_name, labels_data in [("hc_ag6_wknn8", labels_hc_ag6_wknn8), ("hc_ag6", labels_hc_ag6)]:
    valid_indices = labels_data.dropna().index
    if not valid_indices.equals(data_for_metrics.index):
        temp_data = data_for_metrics.loc[labels_data.dropna().index]
        temp_labels = labels_data.dropna()
    else:
        temp_data = data_for_metrics
        temp_labels = labels_data
    temp_labels = temp_labels.astype(int)
    try:
        ch_score = metrics.calinski_harabasz_score(temp_data, temp_labels)
        sil_score = metrics.silhouette_score(temp_data, temp_labels)
        fit_scores.append((cluster_col_name, ch_score, sil_score))
    except ValueError as e:
        print(f"Error al calcular mtricas para {cluster_col_name}: {e}")
        fit_scores.append((cluster_col_name, np.nan, np.nan)) # Aade NaN si hay error
print(fit_scores)
